description: Cameron offers one-stop shopping for your fabrication or contract manufacturing requirements. Cameron has 30+ years of sheet and heavy gauge metal fabrication experience, as well as extensive machining capabilities. We offer custom machinery (design & build), control panels, enclosures, and integrated systems, complimented by Engineering Design Services, which include Product Development from Concept or Reverse-Engineering, to Prototypes to Production runs (with finishes as required) in quantities  from one to several thousand units, From very small components (1 x 1) to large complex systems (10 x 25 x 40). Highly confidential designs and IP protection assured within our tightly secured 125,000 sq. ft. facilities, with NDAs in place as required.  Field Installations, Modifications, and Customer site services are also provided routinely. Specialists in ASME or NACE Certified and Sanitary Welding. Industries serviced include: Mass Transit, Govt./Military Prime Contractors, Avionics, Medical/Pharmaceutical, Food & Dairy, Energy, Glass Mfg., Material Handling, Process Systems, and OEMs. Cameron is ESOP (Employee Owned Company) with 240+ employees.  Contact: Bob Evans or Eric Tobey at sales@camfab.com; (source: ylocal)
